<div class="result <%= @decision.required? ? 'required' : 'not-required' %>">
  <h2><%= @decision.determination %></h2>
  <% if @decision.required? %>
    <p>
      Based on your answers, all three conditions are met: you are a
      Covered Entity or Business Associate, your application handles PHI,
      and third-party vendors process that PHI. A BAA is typically required
      with those vendors.
    </p>
  <% else %>
    <p>
      Based on your answers, not all three conditions are met. A BAA may
      not be required, but you should document your rationale and consult
      qualified counsel.
    </p>
  <% end %>
</div>
<p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
  <a href="/baa-or-not">Start over</a>
</p>
